REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='890', `RecipeID`='890', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Pre-scoop your Ice Cream into separate balls and freeze for a couple hours, this will help it keep form through the recipe In a medium bowl, mix corn flakes, graham crackers, cinnamon, and brown sugar In a separate bowl, mix eggs, sugar, and milk until smooth Dip your ice cream balls into the crumb bowl, then into the eggs, then back into the crumb bowl until fully coated Toss in the freezer for another hour or so Heat your oil up (400F) and fry until golden brown, shouldnt take more than a minute. Top with your favorite toppings and serve!!';
