REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1001', `RecipeID`='1001', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Prepare and cook angel food cake. Cool. Prepare jello and add strawberries, chill in refrigerator until starting to set. In trifle bowl add chunks of angel food cake to form first layer, next layer is jello/strawberry mixture, next layer is cool whip. Repeat layers. Chill until ready to serve.';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1002', `RecipeID`='1002', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='In the blender mix 1 cup of ice, 2 large bananas cut in chunks, 10 strawberries with the stems cut off and 1/4 cup of vanilla yogurt, once blended and 1 more cup of ice and blend again until all mixed and blended. And Thats it your done serve up and enjoy!!';
