REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1080', `RecipeID`='1080', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Get a bowl and a plate, put tortilla chips in a bowl with salsa, lime juice, sour cream and salsa, put plate on top of bowl and shake until chips are seasoned. put chicken and chips on plate, put plain white rice on plate, drizzle with cheese, shake the plate to mix, and sprinkle with salt and pepper. (i like to drizzle it with crushed tortilla chips also) serving size may vary according to how much ingredients you put on.';
