REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1089', `RecipeID`='1089', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Preheat oven to 350°F. In a large bowl, add all the ingredients and mix together with a handheld or stand mixer until smooth. Transfer mixture to a medium baking dish and sprinkle top with remaining 1/4 cup Monterey Jack cheese. Bake until golden and bubbly, 25 to 30 minutes. Garnish with more cilantro and cotija cheese, if desired. Serve with tortilla chips.';
