REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1208', `RecipeID`='1208', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='1. Drain the chicken and spread it across the glass pan (crumbling it up) 2. Mix hot sauce, ranch, and cream cheese in a bowl 3. Pour over the chicken 4. Cover with the cheese 5. Bake at 350 for 25 min or until cheese is brown around the edges 6. Serve with tortilla chips, crunchy bread, or as a sandwich';
