REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1239', `RecipeID`='1239', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='1 Brown Sausage and drain grease. 2 With electric mixer, combine cream cheese and salsa. 3 Add browned sausage to cream cheese mixture. 4 Microwave until warm. 5 Serve with tortilla chips. Tips: I use a glass casserole dish so your sausage doesnt ruin your tupperware container when warming in microwave. If taking this dip to a gathering, it stays nice in a crock pot on low setting.';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1240', `RecipeID`='1240', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='1 In a large skillett add meat, salt& pepper. 2 Brown really well and do not drain meat unless you are using hamburger and the amount of fat is quite a bit. 3 Sprinkle flour over meat and stir well. 4 Once the flour is mixed in well and browned really well, slowly add milk stirring constantly until nice and thick.';
