REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1305', `RecipeID`='1305', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Render the fat from several pieces of smoked bacon (either in the oven or in a pan on the stove) and when cooled add the rendered fat to a clean mason jar. To this add one cup of premium vodka and let steep for several hours to over night. Place the steeped mixture in the freezer for several hours until the fat freezes and can be removed. Strain the remaining liquid several times first through a tea strainer, then through a coffee filter and then through cheese cloth (in order to remove all solids).';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1306', `RecipeID`='1306', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Mix it all together - ENJOY! Here are some other flavor combos  French Vanilla - 2 teaspoons vanilla extract Chocolate Almond - Cocoa Powder and Almond Extract Strudel Cake - 1 Tblsp Cinnamon, Vanilla, and Almond Extract Cinnamon Cake - 2 Tsp Cinnamon, 2 Tsp Vanilla Extract Almond Joy - 1 tsp Coconut Extract, 1 tsp Almond Extract, 2 tblsp Chocolate Syrup Caramel - Just add Caramel lol Honey Vanilla - 1/4 cup honey, 1 tsp Vanilla (yep...that simple) German Strudel - Equal parts Cinnamon, Vanilla, and Almond So many more flavors, experiment!';
