REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='1319', `RecipeID`='1319', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='1 Peel, seed and cut the apple and orange into large chunks. 2 Put the chunks in the blender with the water, and, honey, some sugar, or fake sweeetner, if desired. 3 Blend until it is thick, it takes a minute or two, and I went up to the higest blender setting to get it really smooth. 4 Pour into a glass and have as part of a really healthy breakfast.';
