REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='2797', `RecipeID`='2797', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Combine the dressing ingredients in a blender, using two teaspoons salt and pepper to taste; process until smooth. Combine the salad ingredients in a large bowl and toss with the dressing. Let sit at least 15 minutes before serving, or cover and refrigerate for up to four hours. much more at http://www.arizonafoothillsmagazine.com/taste/phoenix-recipes/recipes-memorial-day-picnic-and-barbecue';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='2798', `RecipeID`='2798', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='In a bowl, combine mayonnaise, sugar, vinegar and salt. Add cucumbers; stir to coat. Cover and refrigerate for 2 hours';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='2799', `RecipeID`='2799', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='In a large salad bowl combine sliced cucumbers, onion and tomatoes. Toss together lightly. In a separate bowl whisk together remaining ingredients. Pour over cucumber mixture. Toss to coat. Refrigerate until chilled. Stir and Serve.';
