REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='3282', `RecipeID`='3282', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='In bowl, combine peanut butter, granola, chopped peanuts, and honey and mix well. Stir in dried cherries. Spread tortillas with softened butter, then spread with peanut butter mixture. Roll up tortillas and cut in half. Serve immediately, or wrap well and freeze. Let thaw in insulated lunch boxes, next to frozen gel pack, until lunchtime.';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='3283', `RecipeID`='3283', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='1 Toast bread. 2 Spread one slice of bread with peanut butter. 3 Spread mayo on top of peanut butter. 4 Top with tomato slices 5 Add 2nd piece of bread, cut in half and enjoy!';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='3284', `RecipeID`='3284', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='1 You will also need: a drinking glass or rolling pin Lay bread on a smooth counter top and use your drinking glass (or rolling pin) to roll over the bread a few times until the bread is flat and make sure you get the edges or crust too. 2 Spread peanut better and jelly on the flattened bread. 3 Roll bread up like a tortilla';
