REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='3339', `RecipeID`='3339', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='1.Make cream of mushroom soup according to the directions on the can. 2.Stir in canned tuna and egg slices. Heat thoroughly. Meanwhile, toast bread slices. 3.Spoon tuna mixture over slices of whole wheat toast. Serve.';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='3340', `RecipeID`='3340', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='1 Place the tofurkey (or turkey) slices on one slice of toasted bread. 2 Place tomato slices on top of tofurkey, and sprinkle salt and pepper on them. 3 Put the avocado slices on top of the tomato and put the other slice of toast on top. 4 Cut in half, eat with fresh melon, and marvel at the glorious simplicity of summer food!';
