REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='3383', `RecipeID`='3383', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Heres another simple snack idea since my other one went over well. Spread a banana with peanut butter, slice into bite size pieces, roll in rice krispie cereal (cocoa krispies would be great too!)';
REPLACE INTO `Directions` SET `ID`='3384', `RecipeID`='3384', `SortOrder`='0', `Directions`='Melt butter or margarine in a 13 x 9-inch baking pan. Blend in next 3 ingredients. Add Spoon Size Shredded Wheat®. Cook and stir gently until cereal is well coated. Bake in a preheated moderate oven (350 degrees F) 15 to 18 minutes or until lightly browned and crisp. Cool. Makes 4 cups.';
